data.description:
***Buyer to receive up to $10k, with acceptable offer, toward closing costs that can be used to buydown the rate!***
Great curb appeal home with no carpet on a good sized, well maintained lot with a large covered patio is ready for new owners. Enjoy the low maintenance LVP and tile floors from the entry all the way through the home. The kitchen opens to the living area which makes for entertaining guest. The spacious primary bedroom is split from the secondary bedrooms, and the primary bath generously lends space for two vanities, a garden tub and separate shower. HVAC replaced this year, and water heater just a few years ago. Located just minutes from TWU & UNT, Lake Lewisville, shops and restaurants, makes it an ideal place to plant roots or would make a great investment. Schedule your showing asap.
